Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:12.58,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}沒有意義的說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:17.92,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}只要開心就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:25.76,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}平平凡凡的每一天
